I always order them in numerical order. Looping tunes first, short tunes, sound effects and then D(PCM) voice samples.<br /><br />If they are not in order I arrange the looping songs together, short tunes, etc. It makes it simple and easy for me.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=43">Gil-Galad</a> — Mon Jun 13, 2011 3:05 pm</p><hr />
